@title Base auction functionality lovingly borrowed from CryptoKitties
 @author Axiom Zen (https://www.axiomzen.co)

We don't want someone to be able to accidentally send funds to this contract so we 
 ensure the fallback function is not payable
@dev Cancels an auction (unconditionally)
